Amiga freeCD: Classic Revolution

"Beneath a Steel Sky" is back on CD-ROM. This graphic adventure brings you into a 
dark-future scenario and is still one of the best games in this genre. It was tested
under OS 3.9, so it should be running on all Amigas. The CD includes the English and
German version for harddisk, but also the diskversion is available.

Also on the CD is the disk-version of "Lure of the Temptress" in English and
German.

